<P>
CSUN SIGNS WOMAN SPRINTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Michelle Barga of Sunnyvale Fremont High has signed a letter of intent to 
attend Cal State Northridge in the fall on a partial track scholarship. 
</P>
<P>
Barga has a personal best of 56.45 seconds in the 400 meters. She competed in 
the state championships at Cerritos College in June but did not qualify for the 
final. 
</P>
</TEXT>
