<TEXT>
<P>
"The Washingtonian" magazine Friday said it was sorry it called the 
presidential pet the ugliest canine in the capital. 
</P>
<P>
"Before you go away for the July 4th weekend, we would like to apologize for 
picking Millie the ugliest dog in Washington," Editor John A. Limpert said in a 
letter delivered Friday to the White House. He also sent a gift of dog biscuits 
to the offended beast. 
</P>
