<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ernie Carr and Tim Murphy have been hired as assistant basketball coaches at UC 
Irvine. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
