<P>
MCLAIN, DENNY; ROSE, PETE; GIAMATTI, A BARTLETT; DOWD, JOHN M; JANSZEN, PAUL; 
PETERS, RON; CINCINNATI REDS (BASEBALL TEAM); INVESTIGATIONS; GAMBLING; MAJOR 
LEAGUE BASEBALL (ORGANIZATION); COMMISSIONER OF BASEBALL 
</P>
