AMERICAN CONTINENTAL CORP; SAVINGS AND LOANS; THRIFTS AND LOANS; INVESTMENTS; 
CALIFORNIA DEPARTMENT OF SAVINGS AND LOANS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
