smolders on the back side of the peak. Photo was taken looking west from Lake 
Elsinore toward Orange County. ; Photo, A state Department of Forestry copter 
drops water on a hot spot in Cleveland National Forest. DON KELSEN / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
