<TEXT>
<P>
Dennis Bradshaw, Michael Hajeck and Gail Itow have joined MicroNet Technology 
as vice presidents. Bradshaw has been appointed vice president and marketing 
director of the company, an Irvine-based data storage products manufacturer. 
Earlier, Bradshaw held positions at CMS Enhancements, AST Research and 
MicroSci. Hajeck was named vice president and sales director. Previously, he 
was with CMS Enhancements where he was involved in sales of data storage 
products. Itow, MicroNet's new controller and vice president of finance, joins 
